Verbs:
a וַיֹּאמֶר דָּוִד אֶל־הַפְּלִשְׁתִּי, OF:אָמַר, say, Conj-w | V-Qal-ConsecImperf-3ms, and_he_said, David, to_the_Philistine, 

b אַתָּה בָּא אֵלַי בְּחֶרֶב וּבַחֲנִית וּבְכִידוֹן, OF:בּוׂא, come, V-Qal-Prtcpl-ms, you, come, to_me, with_sword, and_with_spear, and_with_javelin标枪, 

