d וַיַּךְ אֶת־הַפְּלִשְׁתִּי אֶל־מִצְחוֹ, OF:נָכָה, strike, Conj-w | V-Hifil-ConsecImperf-3ms, and_he_struck, -the_Philistine, in_his_forehead, 

