b: וַיַּךְ אֶת־הַפְּלִשְׁתִּי, OF:נָכָה, strike, Conj-w | V-Hifil-ConsecImperf-3ms, and_he_struck, -the_Philistine, 

c: וַיְמִיתֵהוּ וְחֶרֶב אֵין בְּיַד־דָּוִד, OF:מוּת, die, Conj-w | V-Hifil-ConsecImperf-3ms | 3ms, and_he_killed_him, and_sword, no, in_hand, of_David, 

Translation: And David prevailed over the Philistine with a sling and with a stone, and he struck the Philistine, and he killed him, but no sword in the hand of David. 





